		<span style="color: #000000;">﻿</span>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: x-large;"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;">“表述经典”音乐会</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: large;"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;">时间：2012年11月17日 19:30﻿﻿﻿                  <br />﻿地点：国家大剧院音乐厅               <br /></span></strong></span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: large;"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;">指挥：姜金一（国家一级指挥）<br />首席：唐峰（国家一级演员）      <br />主持：耿靓                                            </span></strong></span></p>
<span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">
 
<p style="text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;"> </p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">一、民族管弦乐《管弦丝竹知多少》                                                             关乃忠曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">二、民族管弦乐《货郎》                                                俄罗斯民间乐曲 赵东升编曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">三、民族管弦乐《蓝色狂想曲》                                       【美】格什温曲  姜莹改编</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                   萨克斯演奏：张克诚</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">四、二胡与乐队《好人一生平安》                                        电视剧《渴望》主题曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                                                          雷蕾曲  陈思昂改编</span></p>
<p class="ListParagraph" style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                    二胡演奏：李源源</span></p>
<p class="ListParagraph" style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">             （国家一级演员、文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获奖者、金钟奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">五、笛子协奏曲《塞外随想》                                              王次恒邵恩曲  刘沙配器</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                    笛子演奏：王次恒</span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">              </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                   （国家一级演员、文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p class="ListParagraph" style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">六、京胡与乐队《赤胆忠心》                            选自现代京剧《智取威虎山》片段</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                                                                   吴华 马骏编曲</span></p>
