<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">                          ——</span></span>——<span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">——</span></span>——        </span>中场休息      <span style="font-family: Calibri;">————<span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">——<span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">——</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">七、琵琶独奏《春雨》                                                                              朱毅 文博曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                    琵琶演奏：于源春</span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                 </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                   （金钟奖获奖者、台北民族器乐协奏大赛金奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">八、民族管弦乐《闹春》                                                                                  朱彬曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">九、 古筝与乐队《渔舟唱晚》                                                         古曲 王甫建改编</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                     古筝演奏：缪青 </span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十、二胡、笛子与乐队《凤凰魅影》            根据电视剧《甄嬛传》插曲改编创作</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                                                          刘欢曲 赵东升改编  </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                            二胡演奏：段超（金钟奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                              笛子演奏：丁晓逵（CCTV民族器乐大赛获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十一、民族管弦乐《第二民族交响乐》                                                          刘星曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                        爵士鼓演奏：朱剑平（文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获奖者）</span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">    </span></p>
